<DATE>940126
</DATE>
<HEADLINE>
FT  26 JAN 94 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Gold shares ended off early highs in line with a further fall in the price
of bullion but remained firm, with the index finally 47 up at 1,957.
Industrials improved 6 to 5,456 and the overall index 24 to 4,763. De Beers
added R2 at R107.
