Securities of the US, was at about 390p per share. Dillon has placed the
shares with other institutions.
The terms of the original acquisition were that any sale of the new shares
by PLA would require the prior consent of IWP. In a statement yesterday, IWP
said it has agreed to the sale of half of the 6m holding, and that the
company welcomed the broadening of its shareholder base.
