<TEXT>
At last a political breakthrough for the followers of the Maharishi Mahesh
Yogi, founder and leading exponent of the business of transcendental
meditation. Having failed with another great transcendental philosophy -
marxism - Joaquim Chissano, Mozambique's president, has taken up the Yogi's
ideas.
