<HEADLINE>
FT  25 JAN 94 / UK Company News: Christies disposes of leasehold interest
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Christies International has completed the disposal of its leasehold interest
in Sussex Mansions, 63-85 Old Brompton Road, South Kensington, London.
The property comprises 40 furnished flats on short lettings and 10 flats on
long underleases with protected tenancies. Consideration is Pounds 9.85m
cash.
</TEXT>
